Features: Operative L-shaped desk with an 18mm thick wooden top in laminate finish and PVC lipping.
Based on metal structure with two curved metal legs formed from 1.5mm metal sheets in electrostatic powder coated paint.
Includes a side with 3 wooden lockable drawers and 2 cabinets with lockable wooden leaves, all in laminate finish.
Optional front modesty panel available in laminate finish.
Features a concealed cable management system with an aluminum flap.
Excludes electric source and grommet power outlet.
Can be matched with corresponding pedestal, credenza, and coffee table leg.

Dimensions: Standard Dimensions: LxWxH 150x170x75 CM Right Or Left side
Alternative Dimension: 170x170x75 CM Right Or Left side
Alternative Dimension: 190x170x75 CM Right Or Left side
